article.description: — Nick Davis' 19 points helped Omaha defeat Stetson 88-80 on Sunday.
article.headline: Davis scores 19, Omaha beats Stetson 88-80
article.story: OMAHA, Neb. -- — Nick Davis' 19 points helped Omaha defeat Stetson 88-80 on Sunday. Davis added seven rebounds for the Mavericks (6-6). Frankie Fidler scored 19 points and added six rebounds. Marquel Sutton had 15 points and shot 5 of 9 from the field and 4 for 5 from the line. The Hatters (6-5) were led in scoring by Jalen Blackmon, who finished with 26 points and three steals. Stephan D. Swenson added 23 points and six rebounds for Stetson. Alec Oglesby also put up 18 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
